e annihilation of WIMPs; nuclear recoils in\ndirect detection; and direct production of the WIMP pair in high-energy\ncolliders. Considering recent evidence in particular for a 130 GeV line from\nthe galactic center, we discuss the detection prospects at upcoming\nexperiments.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 13 Jun 2012 19:54:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 3 Aug 2012 19:34:12 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 26 Mar 2013 13:12:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-03-27"}
