mal states, and, in particular, for systems composed of\nodd number of qubits we find a single configuration of ranks for which there\nare extremal states.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 14 Jun 2012 12:34:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 8 Jul 2012 22:25:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-07-29"}
